# ============================================================
# TRANSPORT CORE RUNTIME
# ============================================================

status: canonical
layer: runtime
domain: transport
scope: transport.core
system: civilization-os
owner: Boss
prepared_by: Zero

## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for transport.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers route visibility,
movement state,
arrival/completion state,
historical transport reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- transport context must resolve
- route basis must resolve
- carried subject scope must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid transport context
- invalid route basis
- invalid carried subject scope
- safe runtime fallback
